OL,3,CCouncil's controversial 'wiggly white
OL,4,Clines' to get new makeover
OL,6,FTwo years since the council spent
OL,7,F#23,000 painting a pedestrianised
OL,8,Fstreet in Worthing - #3million is now
OL,9,Fbeing spent to transform the area.
OL,11,FThe wiggly white lines, painted in
OL,12,FApril 2022, were part of a scheme to
OL,13,Fmake a seaside town in Sussex cleaner,
OL,14,Fgreener and more welcoming. But they
OL,15,Fdivided opinion. While some thought
OL,16,Fthey were 'fun' others called them
OL,17,F'horrendous'.
