OL,4,Clines' to get new makeover
OL,6,FFollowing feedback from residents and
OL,7,Fcommunity groups in Worthing, the
OL,8,Fcouncil says Montague Place will now
OL,9,Fbe transformed into a vibrant green
OL,10,Fspace that links the town to the sea.
OL,12,FFinal designs for the new green space,
OL,13,Fto be called Montague Gardens, have
OL,14,Fnow been revealed.
