OL,3,CCouncil's controversial 'wiggly white
OL,4,Clines' to get new makeover
OL,6,FThe council says the new space has
OL,7,Fbeen inspired by the gardens that
OL,8,Fexisted when Montague Place was first
OL,9,Fbuilt in the early 19th Century. It
OL,10,Fsays the emphasis is on increasing
OL,11,Fbiodiversity with a green space
OL,12,Flinking the seafront to Liverpool
OL,13,FGardens in the north.
OL,15,FA lively social space will be created
OL,16,Fat the north end of the gardens, with
OL,17,Fresidents and visitors welcomed by a
OL,18,Fstand-out Worthing place sign, a green
OL,19,Fliving wall and a performance area.
