OL,4,Clines' to get new makeover
OL,6,FPlans for the site also include the
OL,7,Freplacement of tarmac with accessible
OL,8,Fpaving, 30 new trees, drought-
OL,9,Fresistant planting, a lawn area and
OL,10,Fsociable seating areas.
OL,12,FThe cafe culture will be kept alive
OL,13,Fwith dedicated spaces for businesses
OL,14,Fto have outdoor seating. A new
OL,15,Fhospitality kiosk will be built for
OL,16,Fvendors to serve coffee or ice-cream
OL,17,Ffrom.
