OL,3,CCouncil's controversial 'wiggly white
OL,4,Clines' to get new makeover
OL,6,FYounger children will benefit from a
OL,7,Fnew play area that celebrates
OL,8,FWorthing's seaside heritage and
OL,9,Fhighlights kelp restoration in the
OL,10,Farea. There will be information boards
OL,11,Fon the work to restore natural kelp
OL,12,Fforests as well as tactile fixed play
OL,13,Fequipment.
OL,15,FTo help create a seamless route to the
OL,16,Fsea, the council also plans to move
OL,17,Fthe Marine Parade road crossing to the
OL,18,Fsouthern end of Montague Gardens and
OL,19,Fcreate a new ramp to the promenade,
OL,20,Fsubject to approval from West Sussex
OL,21,FCounty Council.
