OL,3,CCouncil's controversial 'wiggly white
OL,4,Clines' to get new makeover
OL,6,FWork on the new green space, which is
OL,7,Fsubject to full agreement and further
OL,8,Fengagement with partners, is due to
OL,9,Fstart in the autumn and will be
OL,10,Fcompleted in phases over a 15-18 month
OL,11,Fperiod.
OL,13,FThe works will cost just under #3m and
OL,14,Fwill be funded by the Community
OL,15,FInfrastructure Levy (CIL) Strategic
OL,16,FFund.
