OL,3,CCouncil's controversial 'wiggly white
OL,4,Clines' to get new makeover
OL,6,FCllr Caroline Baxter, Worthing's
OL,7,Fcabinet member for regeneration, said,
OL,8,F"Montague Gardens will breathe new
OL,9,Flife into the town centre, boost our
OL,10,Flocal economy, attract visitors and
OL,11,Fprovide residents of all ages with a
OL,12,Fwelcoming space to socialise, have fun
OL,13,Fand enjoy our beautiful town by the
OL,14,Fsea."
